---
layout: layout-base.njk
title: Tools
description: Planning tools for short growing seasons.
canonical: "https://growbydate.com/tools/"
---

<section class="card">
  <h2>Tools</h2>
  <p class="small" style="opacity:0.86;">Fast, practical calculators you can use without accounts or tracking.</p>

  <ul class="list" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
    {%- for t in tools | sort(attribute="order") -%}
      <li class="note">
        <a href="/tools/{{ t.slug }}/"><strong>{{ t.name }}</strong></a>
        {%- if p.data.description -%}
          <div class="small" style="opacity:0.85; margin-top:0.25rem;">{{ t.description }}</div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</section>
